data.description: Welcome  Home to the Boardwalk in Corona: This listing showcases the best of all worlds, as offered for sale for the first time from original owners.  This chic, modern, newer construction gated community presents an urban lifestyle filled with convenience, smart technology, luxury upgrades, and more.  Features of this desirable end-unit include: large entry with bedroom and bath downstairs, a luxurious open floorplan on the main floor with spacious living room, huge kitchen with center island and quartz countertops, dining area with chic modern lighting, corner balcony patio, large wide upgraded shutters, bathrooms on each floor, Owner's Suite and ancillary bedroom on top floor, indoor laundry closet off kitchen, 2-car attached garage, and much more.  The Boardwalk community features pool and spa, cabanas, picnic and BBQ areas, tot-lot, pet park, and walking trails.  And the location is more than convenient, between the 91 & 15 freeways, close to the Corona North Train station, and close to great parks and schools. This warm, cozy, neutral and lovely home will make the heart race -- Schedule your appointment today because this one will be gone quickly.
